Package com.codekutter.zconfig.common

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IConfigurable
    Interface to be implemented by types that can be configurable using a configuration instance.
    IStateEnum<T>
    Interface to be implemented for enums that are used to represent object/process states.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractState<T extends IStateEnum<T>>
    Abstract base class used to define state of objects/instances.
    ClientState
    State instance used for managing client states.
    ConfigProviderFactory
    Factory class to provide config parser and config reader instances.
    ConfigTestConstants  
    ConfigurationAnnotationProcessor
    Helper class to auto-apply configuration values to annotated types.
    ConfigurationAnnotationProcessor.StructFieldAnnotation
    Struct class to pass information about field annotations.
    Context
    Context handle to be used for passing parameters.
    DateTimeUtils
    Utility class to parse/write datetime.
    EnvState
    Class represents a environment state instance.
    FileReadResponse
    Response handle for reading byte data from a file.
    GlobalConstants
    Class defines static global constants.
    JSONConfigConstants
    Class encapsulating the constants defined for processing JSON based configurations.
    LogUtils
    Utility functions for Logging.
    TestJsonTree  
    VariableRegexParser
    Parser to get and set regex replacements for property place holders.
    XMLConfigConstants
    Class encapsulating the constants defined for processing JSON based configurations.
    ZConfigEnv
    Abstract base class for defining the operating environment.
    ZConfigInstance
    Abstract base class for defining a client/server instance.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ConfigProviderFactory.EConfigType
    Enum to define the configuration type.
    EClientState
    State enum to be used for exposing client handle states.
    EEnvState
    State enum representing a environment state.
    LogUtils.ELOGLELVEL
    Enum defining the logging levels.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ConfigurationException
    Exception instance used to raise error in processing configuration requests.
    StateException
    Exception instance used to raise error for state checks.
    ValueParseException
    Exception instance used to raise error when parsing for a specific value type failed.
